name: As nice as purse can be 18
description:
Simple and cute purse, can hold your coins, cash, your cards, ipod... or any other use :)

Each purse is handmade, most of them are (almost) one of a kind due to I chose pieces of fabric from around the world, new ones, vintage or recycled pieces. Every purse is lined with canvas fabric and "ulalá"- label inside.

Front side: vintage fabric.
Back side: vintage fabric.
Zipper: green.

Measures 5.1" wide by 4.1" high or 13x10.5cm
